---
import BaseHead from "../../components/BaseHead.astro";
import SlideHeader from "../../components/SlideHeader.astro";

const title = "UPC Lookup Service";
const description =
	"Today, we'll demonstrate building a simple UPC lookup service that will be based off a real service created for the Community Garden Kitchen of McKinney, TX.";
const permalink =
	"https://slides-astro-cloudflare-upc.codedemos.dev/what-we-are-going-to-build";
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead {title} {description} {permalink} />
	</head>

	<body class=" text-gray-700 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
		<SlideHeader />
		<main class="px-8 mt-32 sm:mt-32 md:mt-16 mb-8">
			<h3 class="text-4xl">UPC Bar Code Lookup Service</h3>
			<p class="mt-8 text-2xl">
				Today we're going to build a simple (fake) UPC lookup service. The user
				will enter a UPC barcode value to get information about the consumer
				product they have scanned.
			</p>

			<p class="mt-8 text-2xl">
				This presentation is based on a <a
					class="underline hover:text-yellow-700"
					href="https://community-garden-kitchen-barcodes.pages.dev/"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer">real UPC lookup service</a> I created for the
				<a
					class="underline hover:text-yellow-700"
					href="https://communitygardenkitchen.org/"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer">Community Garden Kitchen of McKinney</a
				>.
			</p>

			<p class="mt-8 text-2xl">
				If you'd be sound kind as to make a <a
					class="underline hover:text-yellow-700"
					href="https://communitygardenkitchen.org/support/donate/"
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer">donation</a
				>, I would really appreciate it. Your support will help to build and run
				a free restaurant that serves the needs of my community. Anyone in need
				of a meal or some compassionate company will be able to come in and get
				the support they need.
			</p>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
